WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.333 --> 00:00:02.466
Stop for me

2
00:00:02.933 --> 00:00:05.466
Fu Yanling, you are so brave

3
00:00:05.666 --> 00:00:08.200
How dare you bring this woman into my door?

4
00:00:09.466 --> 00:00:10.866
She is your daughter-in-law

5
00:00:10.966 --> 00:00:13.166
What's wrong with me taking her home?

6
00:00:13.166 --> 00:00:14.500
daughter-in-law

7
00:00:15.166 --> 00:00:16.766
As long as I live

8
00:00:16.866 --> 00:00:18.800
I would never have admitted his identity

9
00:00:19.066 --> 00:00:22.566
Get out of here right now

10
00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:25.500
Let's go

11
00:00:26.666 --> 00:00:27.466
Stop

12
00:00:30.366 --> 00:00:31.966
Xia Meng

13
00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:33.766
Aunt Su

14
00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:39.266
Yanli, your marriage partner is Xia Meng

15
00:00:39.266 --> 00:00:40.566
Yeah, what's wrong?

16
00:00:40.566 --> 00:00:41.200
It took half a day

17
00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:43.900
The little white face who married Xia Meng turned out to be my son

18
00:00:43.900 --> 00:00:47.366
Xia Meng, come and sit on the sofa, okay?

19
00:00:49.133 --> 00:00:50.433
Hurry up and do it

20
00:00:50.966 --> 00:00:54.433
Mengmengsu Aunt Butler serves fruit

21
00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:59.366
Dream to eat fruit

22
00:00:59.933 --> 00:01:01.366
Thank you, Aunt Su

23
00:01:04.333 --> 00:01:05.566
What's wrong with my mom?

24
00:01:05.566 --> 00:01:08.466
You ask me, she's your mother, not mine.

25
00:01:09.366 --> 00:01:12.700
Mengmeng, you have married into our Su family

26
00:01:12.900 --> 00:01:16.700
It doesn't seem appropriate to call my aunt again

27
00:01:16.700 --> 00:01:19.833
Should you call me mom?

28
00:01:21.566 --> 00:01:23.666
Why don't you want to?

29
00:01:26.266 --> 00:01:27.100
Mom

30
00:01:28.700 --> 00:01:32.433
Hahaha, come on, give the bride price.

